            time, money, and hassle.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-12">
            <input
            id="waitlist"
              type="email"
              placeholder="Enter your email"
              class="w-full sm:w-80 px-6 py-3 rounded-full border border-gray-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-500"
